<h1>How does the Lightning Network work? Part 1. Building a bi-directional payment channel</h1>

<figure>
<img src="00.webp"/>
</figure>

<p>
Perhaps the Lightning Network is the most anticipated technological novelty for Bitcoin. It is assumed that this payment system, the idea of which was put forward a year ago, will make it possible to carry out a huge number of transactions almost free of charge outside the bitcoyne blockade, and for this one will not have to sacrifice security.
